description:
sizes: M, L, XL

A symbol of elite athletic squads the world over, Nikes Destroyer jacket is well-known for its timeless style and distinction. As an elite fan of Dallas, distinguish yourself from the legions of average fans with your very own Culture Destroyer jacket! Designed with the utmost craftsmanship in mind, this lightweight jacket displays an embroidered Cowboys logo on the chest and embroidered 60 graphics in the left sleeve. To finish this full zip jacket off, its fabric is made from a durable, yet comfortable, polyester and cotton blend. If youre looking for the upper echelon of Dallas gear, youve just found it!
  • 100% Cotton body
  • 65% Polyester/35% Cotton upper back lining
  • Quality embroidery
  • Olympic collar
  • One chest pocket and two front pockets
  • Full button storm flap
  • Imported
  • Officially licensed NFL product
